<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/resetpassword.css">
</head>
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body{
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        #main {
            position: relative;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            overflow: hidden;
          }
          #left {
            position: relative;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgb(11, 15, 36);
          }
          #left #img{
              position: relative;
              top: 15%;
              left: 20%;
              width: 13%;
              height: 13%;
              transform: rotate(1deg);
              /* background-color: red; */
              /* box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px 10px blue; */
          }
          #img img{
            position: relative;
              width: 100%;
              height: 100%;
          }
          #left h1{
              position: relative;
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              color: white;
              top: 17%;
              left: 22%;
              /* background-color: red; */
              width: 50%;
              font-weight: 500;
              letter-spacing: 1px;
          }
          #left p{
              position: relative;
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.484);
              top: 20%;
              left: 22%;
              line-height: 24px;
          }
          #left p:nth-child(4){
              margin-top: 30px;
          }
          #left a{
              position: relative;
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              text-decoration: none;
              color: rgba(169, 83, 249, 0.861);
              top: 30%;
              left: 22%;
              font-size: 17px;
              font-weight: 500;
              letter-spacing: 1px;
          }
          #left a:hover{
            text-decoration: underline;
          }
          #right {
            position: relative;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgb(11, 15, 36);
            /* border-left: 0.3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.142); */
            box-shadow: -50px 0px 20px 0px rgb(2, 2, 25);
          }
          #right #img{
              position: relative;
              top: 10%;
              left: 12%;
              width: 20%;
              height: 20%;
              transform: rotate(-50deg);
              /* background-color: red; */
              /* box-shadow: 10px 10px 10px 10px blue; */
          }
          #img img{
            position: relative;
              width: 100%;
              height: 100%;
          }
          #right h1{
              position: relative;
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              color: white;
              top: 10%;
              left: 15%;
              /* background-color: red; */
              width: 50%;
              font-weight: 500;
              letter-spacing: 1px;
          }
          form{
              position: relative;
              top: 15%;
              left: 15%;
              width: 45%;
              height: 30%;
              /* background-color: red; */
          }
          #password{
              position: relative;
              width: 100%;
              height: 25%;
              background-color: rgba(48, 49, 57, 0.285); 
              padding: 0% 15px;
              display: flex;
              flex-direction: column;
              justify-content: space-between;
              border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(184, 16, 251, 0.756);
              border-top-left-radius: 5px;
              border-top-right-radius: 5px;
          }
          label{
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              color: rgba(184, 16, 251, 0.753);
              font-size: 15px;
              letter-spacing: 1px;  
              margin-top: 5px; 
          }
          input{
              position: relative;
              width: 100%;
              height: 32px;
              border: none;
              background: none;
              outline: none;
              font-size: 20px;
              color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.537);

          }
          #cnfrmpassword{
              position: relative;
              width: 100%;
              height: 24%;
              background-color: rgba(48, 49, 57, 0.285); 
              padding: 0% 15px;
              margin-top: 30px;
              color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.537);
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              letter-spacing: 1px;
              border-radius: 5px;
          }
          #btn{
              position: relative;
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              font-size: 17px;
              width: 52%;
              height: 45px;
              background-color: rgba(137, 43, 226, 0.861);
              color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.884);
              border-radius: 25px;
              margin-top: 30px;
          }
          #right a{
              position: relative;
              font-family: "Aeonik";
              font-size: 16px;
              text-decoration: none;
              word-spacing: -1px;
              left: 46%;
              top: 9.5%;
              font-weight: 500;
              color: rgba(169, 83, 249, 0.861);
              letter-spacing: 0.3px;
          }
          #right a:hover{
              color: rgba(137, 43, 226, 0.861);
              text-decoration: underline;
          }
    </style>
<body>
    <div id="main">
        <div id="left">
            <div id="img">
                <!-- <img style="background-color: black;" src="" alt=""> -->
            </div>
            
            <h1>Check your email</h1>
            <p>if an account exists for <span style="color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.808);">a.fedorov@email.com</span>,<br>you'll receive an email with a reset password link. </p>
            <p>Check your inbox and follow the reset link.</p>

            <a href="/login">Return to login</a>
        </div>
        <div id="right">
            <div id="img">
                <!-- <img src="./32853260-removebg-preview.png" alt=""> -->
            </div>
            <h1>Set new password</h1>
        <form action="/reset/<%= user.id %>" method="post">
            <div id="password">
                <label for="">New password</label>
                <input type="password" name="newpassword">
            </div>
            <input id="cnfrmpassword" type="password" placeholder="Confirm your password">
            <input id="btn" type="submit" value="Set new password">
        </form>
        <a href="/login">Go to login page</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>